---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro'
import Hero from '../../components/Hero.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="About Me">
  <Header />
  <Hero
    headline="About"
    lede="I'm a Product Designer and Frontend Engineer focused on creating amazing products and services."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <article class="panel">
      <p>
        I studied Biotechnology, Engineering and Communications, but my love for design 
        was always greater.
      </p>
      <p>
        I'm a passionate photographer who loves to understand and repair old cameras.
        I'm a devotee of analog film processes.
      </p>
      <p>
        I believe we can't look to the future without understanding our present. Context
        shapes our ability to foresee what's next. Design should embrace science, art and society,
        stand on the shoulders of technology, and look into our history to create a story
        we can all relate to, as one of my favourite designers once said:
      </p>
      <blockquote>"Design is not added value; design IS value." — Gui Bonsiepe</blockquote>
      <p>
        I've held a variety of design roles since the late 1990s. My background begins with 
        the Ulm Model and grows every day as technology, philosophy and arts evolve.
      </p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <article class="panel">
      <h4>Contact me</h4>
      <p>
        I'm looking to work with amazing people and meaningful projects. <br> If you think someone
        like me would be a good fit, let me know.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="mailto:hello@pablonoel.com">hello@pablonoel.com</a>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Github</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Medium</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
